From: Dong Aisheng <aisheng.dong@nxp.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Sep 2021 17:06:20 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] remoteproc: imx_rproc: Fix rsc-table name
Git-commit: e90547d59d4e29e269e22aa6ce590ed0b41207d2
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc1
References: git-fixes stable-5.14.19

Usually the dash '-'  is preferred in node name.
So far, not dts in upstream kernel, so we just update node name
in driver.

